    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥 <strong>Why it’s spore-tacular </strong>💥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>Grow stronger every run!</strong> Each failed invasion feeds the forest. Unlock new Shrooms, discover new biomes, and activate powerful modifiers that twist every run into something new. Your tiny fungi grow tougher each attempt… even if the trees don’t survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>No cookie-cutter maps!</strong> Every island is procedurally generated with shifting rivers, dense forests, and natural choke points that force you to rethink your strategy every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>Nature fights dirty!</strong> Poisonous Shrooms, exploding Shrooms, storm-summoning Shrooms, every species has its own wild powers and playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>No lanes, no rails!</strong> Lumberjacks wander freely, carving their own roads and bridges as they go. Defend from every angle, not just a straight line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>Axe-wielding weirdos!</strong> Speedy sprinters, flamethrower fanatics, jetpack junkies, and massive boss jacks, every enemy brings a new headache.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 <strong>Bend the battle your way!</strong> Unleash player-controlled abilities, stack game-changing modifiers, and take on skill-testing challenges that shake up every run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🪓 <strong>Jacks keep coming, you keep Shrooming</strong> 🪓</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two invasions are ever the same. Each run brings new islands, new enemy paths, and new decisions — where to build, what to sacrifice, and how to make those lumberjacks deeply regret picking up an axe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wave after wave, they’ll burn, chop, and bulldoze everything in sight. You won’t save every tree… but you <i>can</i> make sure every jack pays for every splinter.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/eac64a91c6fc7b91b4e099414a618ae5.poster.avif?t=1767895385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/eac64a91c6fc7b91b4e099414a618ae5.webm?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/eac64a91c6fc7b91b4e099414a618ae5.mp4?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 <strong>Unleash devastating player-controlled abilities!</strong> 🎯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick off enemies with pinpoint snipers, unleash sweeping area blasts, and lay traps anywhere on the island to stop the jacks in their tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/dd68d50019e4a030446cc13d15e66ad1.poster.avif?t=1767895385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/dd68d50019e4a030446cc13d15e66ad1.webm?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/dd68d50019e4a030446cc13d15e66ad1.mp4?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍄 <strong>Turbo-charge your Shrooms </strong>🍄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Shroom evolves along a unique upgrade path, unlocking powerful passives and monstrous abilities. Then stack game-changing modifiers to push every build even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/3b283249515e46ee5d145ac211447767.poster.avif?t=1767895385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/3b283249515e46ee5d145ac211447767.webm?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/3b283249515e46ee5d145ac211447767.mp4?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌲 <strong>Endless islands to defend </strong>🌲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle across endlessly generated islands and unlock new biomes to face ever-deadlier threats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/085465ab96a473b266d96736bb191d00.poster.avif?t=1767895385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/085465ab96a473b266d96736bb191d00.webm?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310170/extras/085465ab96a473b266d96736bb191d00.mp4?t=1767895385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Music by Zoe Wynns (Contagonist)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
